Maria Margaretha, Princess of Saxony Gender: F

Bio/autobiography

Rodden Rating B Collector: Scholfield

Astrology data 19°38' 17°02 Asc. 11°41'

Biography

Princess of Poland, Lithuania and Saxony, as the daughter of Augustus III of Poland, Elector of Saxony (as Friedrich Augustus I), King of Poland and Grand Duke of Lithuania (as August II). Her mother Maria Josepha, born an Archduchess of Austria. She died on 1 February 1734, aged 6.

Source Notes

Sy Scholfield quotes from "Grosses vollständiges Universal-Lexicon aller Wissenschafften und Künste' by Carl Günther Ludovici (J. H. Zedler, 1739), p. 1471: "Marie Margarethe Francisce Xaverie ... ward gebohren am 13 September 1727. früh um 2 Uhr zu Dressden un Schlosse."

Translation: Marie Margarthe Francisce Xaverie ... was born on 13 September 1727 early in the day at 2 o'clock at Dresden castle.
